00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,930
<font color="yellow">Yesterday</font>

7
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:38,470
<font color="yellow">Love was such an easy game to play</font>

8
00:00:39,260 --> 00:00:42,660
<font color="yellow">Now I need a place to hide away</font>

9
00:00:43,530 --> 00:00:49,320
<font color="yellow">Oh, I believe in yesterday</font>

10
00:00:59,590 --> 00:01:00,590
