<font color="yellow">but it's hard to learn at my age.</font>

13
00:01:07,190 --> 00:01:08,320
<font color="yellow">Are you married?</font>

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:13,020
<font color="yellow">I was widowed five years ago.</font>

15
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:17,060
<font color="yellow">I have a son who is in university.</font>

16
00:01:20,690 --> 00:01:22,120
<font color="yellow">I was widowed, too.</font>

17
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:24,860
<font color="yellow">It happened long time ago.</font>

18
00:01:26,460 --> 00:01:27,660
<font color="yellow">I'm alone now.</font>

19
00:01:29,590 --> 00:01:31,720
<font color="yellow">I have a daughter who's almost 40 years old.</font>

20
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:35,890
<font color="yellow">Right. I have my parents and a brother, too.</font>

21
00:01:36,490 --> 00:01:38,990
<font color="yellow">I'm not alone, I guess.</font>

22
00:01:46,290 --> 00:01:48,190
<font color="yellow">The street lamps</font>

23
00:01:49,490 --> 00:01:51,590
<font color="yellow">On the alleyways</font>

24
00:01:54,390 --> 00:01:58,260
<font color="yellow">Are turning on one by one</font>

25
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:01,990
<font color="yellow">Beyond the scarlet sunset</font>

26
