<font color="yellow">The day has gone by again</font>

27
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:10,690
<font color="yellow">Everything feels like it was a dream</font>

28
00:02:12,390 --> 00:02:15,190
<font color="yellow">I miss you so</font>

29
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:19,230
<font color="yellow">Just the way you were</font>

30
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:21,260
<font color="yellow">As if nothing</font>

31
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:25,560
<font color="yellow">Ever happened at all</font>

32
00:02:29,490 --> 00:02:30,660
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

33
00:02:34,090 --> 00:02:36,620
<font color="yellow">Ma'am, your card!</font>

34
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:39,090
<font color="yellow">- I'm sorry. Thank you.
- No problem.</font>

35
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,890
<font color="yellow">Are there any tickets left?</font>

36
00:02:51,490 --> 00:02:52,890
<font color="yellow">I really have to go.</font>

37
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:55,320
<font color="yellow">We only have business seats left.</font>

38
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:56,960
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

39
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:03,620
<font color="yellow">I'll take it.</font>

40
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:09,940
<font color="yellow">- Yes.
- Did I tell you that...</font>

41
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:11,150
<font color="yellow">Jeong A is getting a divorce?</font>

42
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:13,060
<font color="yellow">- You did.
- What do you think about it?</font>

43
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:17,070
<font color="yellow">I think she's finally taking her revenge.</font>

44
00:03:17,070 --> 00:03:18,590
<font color="yellow">I don't think she'll actually do it.</font>

45
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:19,760
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

46
00:03:20,090 --> 00:03:22,320
<font color="yellow">She already found a new place.</font>

47
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,690
<font color="yellow">Seok Gyun doesn't know about it.</font>

48
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:26,960
<font color="yellow">We're going over to clean the place tomorrow.</font>

49
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,950
<font color="yellow">- Come with me.
- Not again.</font>

50
00:03:28,950 --> 00:03:31,170
<font color="yellow">Don't make me regret making up with you.</font>

51
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:33,420
<font color="yellow">Just date a guy instead.</font>

52
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:35,830
<font color="yellow">Don't be so obsessed with me.</font>

53
00:03:41,370 --> 00:03:42,430
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

54
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,770
<font color="yellow">Hold on.</font>

55
00:03:46,330 --> 00:03:49,030
<font color="yellow">What else should we take to help her clean?</font>

56
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:51,730
<font color="yellow">I guess you and Wan talked it out.</font>

57
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,800
<font color="yellow">It was a misunderstanding about Dong Jin.</font>

58
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,470
<font color="yellow">Now, I'm the only crazy one.</font>

59
00:03:58,300 --> 00:04:01,270
<font color="yellow">It's her fault for making you misunderstand. It's not your fault.</font>

60
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,590
<font color="yellow">Anyway, it feels good to pull out her hair.</font>

61
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:07,630
<font color="yellow">She screamed and told me that she hated me.</font>

62
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:14,000
<font color="yellow">She probably only said it out of spite, right?</font>

63
00:04:14,370 --> 00:04:18,300
<font color="yellow">Well, it's not like I adore her all the time either.</font>

64
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,070
<font color="yellow">I guess it's the same.</font>

65
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,600
<font color="yellow">Contrary to what most mums think,</font>

66
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,570
<font color="yellow">kids usually hate their mums.</font>

67
00:04:25,330 --> 00:04:26,630
<font color="yellow">I like my mum.</font>

68
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:28,870
<font color="yellow">That's because you got older. You weren't like that before.</font>

69
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:31,600
<font color="yellow">That's true. Mum was a nightmare.</font>

70
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:35,870
<font color="yellow">There is no truce between a mother and a child...</font>

71
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:37,270
<font color="yellow">until you're on your deathbed.</font>

72
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:40,800
<font color="yellow">When you're about to die, Wan will love you a lot.</font>

73
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,770
<font color="yellow">She might even cry her eyes out.</font>

74
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:44,770
<font color="yellow">Let's look forward to that day.</font>

75
00:04:45,370 --> 00:04:49,230
<font color="yellow">If anyone wants to be loved by their kid, I guess they should die.</font>

76
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:56,380
<font color="yellow">Hey, Choong Nam. Should I start dating?</font>

77
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:57,490
<font color="yellow">That's what I want to ask.</font>

78
00:04:57,490 --> 00:05:00,070
<font color="yellow">There's a guy, you know?</font>

79
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:02,170
<font color="yellow">He's 10 years younger.</font>

80
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:05,780
<font color="yellow">I've been just eyeing him.</font>

81
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:07,000
<font color="yellow">I think he's quite all right.</font>

82
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,500
<font color="yellow">This is amazing.</font>

83
00:05:14,370 --> 00:05:15,740
<font color="yellow">It's hot.</font>

84
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,540
<font color="yellow">Here, you didn't even have dinner.</font>

85
00:05:18,130 --> 00:05:20,400
<font color="yellow">Fill yourself up with this.</font>

86
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,630
<font color="yellow">Be careful, it's hot.</font>

87
00:05:25,330 --> 00:05:27,500
<font color="yellow">I wish it rained more.</font>

88
00:05:28,170 --> 00:05:29,170
<font color="yellow">I know, right?</font>

89
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,500
<font color="yellow">I wish it would rain more.</font>

90
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:34,600
<font color="yellow">It's just drizzling.</font>

91
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:39,130
<font color="yellow">I wish it would rain...</font>

92
00:05:39,530 --> 00:05:42,170
<font color="yellow">like cats and dogs...</font>

93
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:45,030
<font color="yellow">so that the two of us are stuck here.</font>

94
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:48,590
<font color="yellow">I want to be stuck here for three months...</font>

95
00:05:48,590 --> 00:05:50,330
<font color="yellow">and just stay with you.</font>

96
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,600
<font color="yellow">It's hot.</font>

97
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:55,400
<font color="yellow">Eat or talk. Just do one at a time.</font>

98
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,130
<font color="yellow">Why are you so rushed?</font>

99
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:00,530
<font color="yellow">It's because I like you.</font>

100
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:03,170
<font color="yellow">Gosh.</font>

101
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:06,630
<font color="yellow">It must be good to like me.</font>

102
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,800
<font color="yellow">I don't like or hate anything now that I'm old.</font>

103
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:17,100
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

104
00:06:19,170 --> 00:06:20,900
<font color="yellow">You have some on you.</font>

105
00:06:21,700 --> 00:06:22,700
<font color="yellow">It's off.</font>

106
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:26,870
<font color="yellow">You have some, too.</font>

107
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,870
<font color="yellow">Back then,</font>

108
00:06:34,700 --> 00:06:36,630
<font color="yellow">we were doing something like this...</font>

109
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,700
<font color="yellow">before we kissed.</font>

110
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:42,300
<font color="yellow">I did the same thing with my late husband.</font>

111
00:06:43,170 --> 00:06:47,130
<font color="yellow">Why did you have to break the mood?</font>

112
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:50,070
<font color="yellow">Why did you have to mention him?</font>

113
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:52,200
<font color="yellow">Why did you bring him up?</font>

114
00:06:57,270 --> 00:07:00,070
<font color="yellow">- Gosh.
- Are you going to sleep there?</font>

115
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:03,070
<font color="yellow">If you don't want to share a room with me,</font>

116
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:05,200
<font color="yellow">go to that chilly room and sleep.</font>

117
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:08,770
<font color="yellow">Gosh. Here.</font>

118
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:12,500
<font color="yellow">If I go over the line...</font>

119
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:15,170
<font color="yellow">I'll bring the axe from outside...</font>

120
00:07:15,170 --> 00:07:16,570
<font color="yellow">and cut you.</font>

121
00:07:20,700 --> 00:07:22,600
<font color="yellow">Your husband, Jung Cheol...</font>

122
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:25,830
<font color="yellow">What was he like to you?</font>

123
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:34,770
<font color="yellow">Other than cheating on me once, he was a good man.</font>

124
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:38,070
<font color="yellow">I guess he didn't cheat on you more than once.</font>

125
00:07:39,330 --> 00:07:40,600
<font color="yellow">Are there such people?</font>

126
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,890
<font color="yellow">Are you one of them?</font>

127
00:07:42,890 --> 00:07:45,030
<font color="yellow">No. I'm the type that women fell for.</font>

128
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,600
<font color="yellow">I wasn't like that.</font>

129
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,100
<font color="yellow">What was your wife like?</font>

130
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,470
<font color="yellow">She was beautiful.</font>

131
00:07:54,470 --> 00:07:57,280
<font color="yellow">Tell me more. What was she like?</font>

132
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:59,770
<font color="yellow">I just told you. She was beautiful.</font>

133
00:08:01,330 --> 00:08:03,770
<font color="yellow">She was a little sensitive,</font>

134
00:08:04,530 --> 00:08:06,030
<font color="yellow">but it wasn't a big deal.</font>

135
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:09,330
<font color="yellow">I heard you quit your job for three years...</font>

136
00:08:09,330 --> 00:08:11,500
<font color="yellow">to take care of her when she was sick.</font>

137
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,500
<font color="yellow">I did.</font>

138
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,200
<font color="yellow">I loved those three years.</font>

139
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:21,970
<font color="yellow">I used to love whistling, just like you.</font>

140
00:08:25,130 --> 00:08:27,600
<font color="yellow">If you're trying to charm me with your whistling,</font>

141
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:29,780
<font color="yellow">she can here you from up there.</font>

142
00:08:29,780 --> 00:08:31,970
<font color="yellow">She would be cheering me on.</font>

143
00:08:32,370 --> 00:08:35,300
<font color="yellow">She'd think I made a nice new friend.</font>

144
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:36,800
<font color="yellow">You wish.</font>

145
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:42,640
<font color="yellow">What is it? Do you think your husband wouldn't like it?</font>

146
00:08:44,570 --> 00:08:46,140
<font color="yellow">Were you good to her?</font>

147
00:08:48,830 --> 00:08:49,970
<font color="yellow">Only after she got sick.</font>

148
00:08:50,930 --> 00:08:54,230
<font color="yellow">I didn't care about her much before then.</font>

149
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,670
<font color="yellow">Husbands...</font>

150
00:08:57,700 --> 00:09:00,970
<font color="yellow">grow up when their wives get sick.</font>

151
00:09:02,730 --> 00:09:03,930
<font color="yellow">What morons.</font>

152
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,930
<font color="yellow">When was...</font>

153
00:09:07,140 --> 00:09:09,030
<font color="yellow">the happiest day in your life?</font>

154
00:09:11,770 --> 00:09:13,470
<font color="yellow">The day my eldest was born.</font>

155
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:18,570
<font color="yellow">When was the saddest day then?</font>

156
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,930
<font color="yellow">When my eldest died.</font>

157
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:30,770
<font color="yellow">Min Ho's my second son.</font>

158
00:09:32,730 --> 00:09:34,730
<font color="yellow">It was just a fever.</font>

159
00:09:38,530 --> 00:09:41,140
<font color="yellow">We lived near my husband's home town.</font>

160
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:44,770
<font color="yellow">He was on a business trip,</font>

161
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:49,070
<font color="yellow">so I carried our son all the way to the hospital.</font>

162
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:51,930
<font color="yellow">But they said...</font>

163
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:54,930
<font color="yellow">he was already dead.</font>

164
00:09:55,770 --> 00:09:57,770
<font color="yellow">I couldn't believe it.</font>

165
00:10:10,330 --> 00:10:11,930
<font color="yellow">I carried my dead son...</font>

166
00:10:12,770 --> 00:10:14,570
<font color="yellow">and walked and walked along...</font>

167
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:18,170
<font color="yellow">a path lined by trees.</font>

168
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:20,500
<font color="yellow">I kept walking.</font>

169
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:29,170
<font color="yellow">He was so cute.</font>

170
00:10:32,330 --> 00:10:35,330
<font color="yellow">He had double eyelids, just like me.</font>

171
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:41,640
<font color="yellow">Let's stop. I miss him now.</font>

172
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:47,030
<font color="yellow">You know,</font>

173
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:50,370
<font color="yellow">I don't fear death one bit.</font>

174
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:52,800
<font color="yellow">I'll be reunited...</font>

175
00:10:53,230 --> 00:10:55,530
<font color="yellow">with my husband and the people I miss.</font>

176
00:11:01,170 --> 00:11:02,670
<font color="yellow">You aged so beautifully,</font>

177
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:06,830
<font color="yellow">so I thought you'd had an uneventful life.</font>

178
00:11:09,370 --> 00:11:12,270
<font color="yellow">But then, no life...</font>

179
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,730
<font color="yellow">is truly uneventful.</font>

180
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,230
<font color="yellow">Did you really want to see me?</font>

181
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:24,200
<font color="yellow">Every now and then...</font>

182
00:11:26,130 --> 00:11:28,800
<font color="yellow">I'd wonder how you'd be doing.</font>

183
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:30,820
<font color="yellow">How honest.</font>

184
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:32,830
<font color="yellow">I wouldn't have believed it if you said, "all the time".</font>

185
00:11:33,370 --> 00:11:37,170
<font color="yellow">Growing old changes you in a way you don't like.</font>

186
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:41,130
<font color="yellow">If I were younger,</font>

187
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,830
<font color="yellow">even if you slapped...</font>

188
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:47,730
<font color="yellow">or attacked me with an axe,</font>

189
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:54,130
<font color="yellow">I would've still tried to hug you until our ribs broke.</font>

190
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:56,930
<font color="yellow">I can't now.</font>

191
00:11:58,830 --> 00:12:01,370
<font color="yellow">I'm just too sleepy to.</font>

192
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:08,630
<font color="yellow">Let's see the sunrise tomorrow.</font>

193
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:11,270
<font color="yellow">Okay. Goodnight.</font>

194
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,070
<font color="yellow">Who's there?</font>

195
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:54,030
<font color="yellow">(Sharpening the Blade of Revenge, Part 1)</font>

196
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,670
<font color="yellow">Are you cold?</font>

197
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:05,770
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

198
00:13:06,230 --> 00:13:07,600
<font color="yellow">If you're tired,</font>

199
00:13:08,470 --> 00:13:09,770
<font color="yellow">I can carry you.</font>

200
00:13:09,770 --> 00:13:12,400
<font color="yellow">I'm still pretty strong. Get on my back.</font>

201
00:13:13,570 --> 00:13:14,630
<font color="yellow">I'm serious.</font>

202
00:13:16,330 --> 00:13:17,530
<font color="yellow">Carry me, then.</font>

203
00:13:17,530 --> 00:13:18,970
<font color="yellow">- What?
- Carry me.</font>

204
00:13:25,130 --> 00:13:26,170
<font color="yellow">Just walk.</font>

205
00:13:27,300 --> 00:13:29,900
<font color="yellow">I used to be able to carry you.</font>

206
00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:31,700
<font color="yellow">Do you remember?</font>

207
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:35,030
<font color="yellow">You were asleep one night, but I woke you up...</font>

208
00:13:35,530 --> 00:13:39,470
<font color="yellow">and carried you all the way up a mountain.</font>

209
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:42,770
<font color="yellow">You kissed me first that day.</font>

210
00:13:44,230 --> 00:13:45,700
<font color="yellow">It must've been your wife.</font>

211
00:13:46,570 --> 00:13:48,610
<font color="yellow">We'd gotten into a fight...</font>

212
00:13:48,610 --> 00:13:52,100
<font color="yellow">and took separate buses to go home.</font>

213
00:13:53,730 --> 00:13:55,400
<font color="yellow">I don't like it.</font>

214
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:58,700
<font color="yellow">You brought your wife to a place we went to.</font>

215
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:02,400
<font color="yellow">This isn't the place I brought my wife to.</font>

216
00:14:02,830 --> 00:14:04,130
<font color="yellow">It's fine.</font>

